{"title":"Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofagico","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología/Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofagico-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Enfermedad por Reflujo\\NGastroesofagico","guid":"-0GZIb1VnFkcWJEw_Zw_ug","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"INTRODUCCIÓN","guid":"Gq6XfyNKZiI_zm32SQJJ-w","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Reflujo gastroesofágico\\Nfisiológico:","guid":"oEzhwUsxRwYsiXHV9pYdTw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Frecuencia postprandial.","guid":"xZeWDL3sVTBGY3Nk4Gw9gw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Duración breve.","guid":"r3HiBVrEAOr5NZCZB2UoTA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"• Asintomático.","guid":"yiMtQCrfMbyCxfHgGr3WeA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"• Raro durante el sueño.","guid":"cv1T4CfkyrognGFln0cFzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"• Reflujo\\Npatológico:","guid":"qSfThjb3Ul5FdmMZgEL3jQ","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Asociado a síntomas o lesión mucosa (esofagitis).","guid":"Ck7EcJYo3DC3d5KQeC4mrw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Frecuente durante la noche.","guid":"wN3FKlK4_Y3-m2h7YY44RQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"• ERGE (enf. de reflujo\\Ngastroesofágico):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Síntomas sugestivos de reflujo.","guid":"wkDlo_YSpobEkAroqbN5fA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Complicaciones posibles.","guid":"u8GiN7pUhlnZJD0qNKM2GA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"• No necesariamente inflamación esofágica.","guid":"uX6QCi5RNXKd0EzsOjfOvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"• Esofagitis por\\Nreflujo:","guid":"4BCYAETD8_oLsA4mXxVRqw","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Subgrupo de ERGE con evidencia endoscópica de erosiones esofágicas.","guid":"BEP7i074RDLYnrRzBh5YmA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Clasificación de Los Ángeles: descripciones de roturas mucosas.","guid":"dLOYr7oCTPIzrly0CDc-cA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Generalmente confinadas a la unión gastroesofágica.","guid":"VqCoybYVJWUxMHld4kVAFw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"MECANISMOS DE LA ENFERMEDAD POR\\NREFLUJO GASTROESOFÁGICO (ERGE)","guid":"Qxt7GqIJEG2zY4WfWSqlGQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Algoritmo 1:","guid":"uSG_JX_IuHg4C8BU97Uq0w","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Desequilibrio\\Nentre:","guid":"sZEcYN9W5yJbIkY-RQ5x7w","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Factores\\Nlesivos/sintomáticos:","guid":"E6NGwBuQoNhv7dlLdMy7Ow","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Eventos de reflujo.","guid":"CzFtW_i_pwvhKBMQtskKTA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Acidez del reflujo.","guid":"NMcea3mAmhBkPzx748AoGA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• Sensibilidad esofágica.","guid":"CXEKO2k_J-hh_iA6enWFhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"• Factores\\Ndefensivos:","guid":"Ge9yOJofmjY5wgO3qq3PDw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Aclaramiento ácido esofágico.","guid":"Z6UvyoH_sRPEJGkTJQB6mw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Integridad mucosa.","guid":"sdcWz1P0B8jAmfHAib4KJQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"19","text":"• Lesión mucosa ↔ frecuencia de eventos de reflujo, duración de la acidificación mucosa esofágica y potencia cáustica del líquido refluido.","guid":"u3P5KnqYK0X9NAUmE-OAPQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"19","text":"• Gravedad de síntomas ↔ frecuencia y duración de eventos + hipersensibilidad esofágica (2, 3, 4).","guid":"2Ee3fEcOa8DiUbkzjxwDqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"18","text":"Esofagitis:","guid":"fcAMLgzcDWo8fK1v6BH2Bw","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Inflamación mediada por citocinas, no por efecto químico directo de la exposición prolongada a ácido, pepsina y bilis\\N(“hipótesis de quemadura”) (5-7).","guid":"xjiYxtCoidFtv27IU878yA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Observación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Eventos histopatológicos (inflamación linfocítica, espacios intercelulares dilatados) ↔ ocurren en el epitelio profundo.","guid":"AZEgWZ2pNKExReIkNMwXAA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Cambios regenerativos (hiperplasia de células basales, elongación papilar) ↔ inician antes de la necrosis superficial.","guid":"4WPg-LmQ2NxdCbEj3sXnzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"• Inflamación mediada por citocinas ↔ alteraciones en la permeabilidad mucosa y sensibilidad esofágica sin esofagitis.","guid":"spxa1aUOYRYVyiSh7l-Hng","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"BARRERA\\NANTIRREFLUJO","guid":"V5irtiGbNgk0tNRHQo9l9g","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"ERGE (enfermedad por\\Nreflujo gastroesofágico)","guid":"LxKx-FlAJgL_8h1RCjDcPg","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Espectro que incluye:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Esofagitis por reflujo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• ERGE no erosiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"• ERGE extraesofágica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"• Hipersensibilidad al reflujo.","guid":"1KHvzdkuoyhEVnePz_M5iw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"• Esófago de Barrett (4).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"36","text":"Disfunción de la\\Nbarrera antirreflujo:","guid":"YomDo965GXTWaRlaMO_kvQ","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Mayor en esofagitis o secuelas de esofagitis y ERGE no erosiva con exposición anormal al ácido esofágico en pH-metría (8).","guid":"rJ4QJusQGKYIWJaUBq_jwg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Esofagitis de alto grado (Los Ángeles C o D) ↔ mayor disfunción que esofagitis de bajo grado (Los Ángeles A o B) (9).","guid":"Og29KLGfeLxa8AOJTL3_FA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Barrera\\Nantirreflujo:","guid":"SLnXZ9Gg_nabCGHqQBFIxg","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Previene reflujo gástrico\\Nal esófago distal durante:","guid":"AjLhZ9XFWtkxSimS6cat3Q","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Decúbito.","guid":"J-rMn0cWGl6bLMFVIlioGw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Aumento brusco de presión intraabdominal.","guid":"kYT8QyKDuUkiG3nTMyiU9w","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Relajación inducida por deglución del EEI (esfínter esofágico inferior).","guid":"niHjgxFFOE1_m7ubSUmPqQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"36","text":"Conceptos principales de\\Ncompetencia de la barrera antirreflujo:","guid":"G3oCjRiiTHt33Lx2HIzxjg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"1. EEI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Esfínter esofágico intrínseco.","guid":"i0y5EEBC_9v17sf9bdzlbA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"• Fibras de honda gástrica y músculo circular esofágico distal forman un “nudo” alrededor de la unión gastroesofágica (10-13).","guid":"auD1f45NjXJ9bWDDDX_jzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"2. Diafragma\\Ncrural:","guid":"jA-ZxXpGJKNhIO2veDartw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• Esfínter extrínseco.","guid":"e7os6PkD80Du6SyJ5mZxcw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"• Contracción rápida y vigorosa.","guid":"IXzRvFOuq_zN9VOfEIDIzQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"• Angula el esófago en la unión gastroesofágica durante inspiración y esfuerzo abdominal (14-15).","guid":"1bSS7CNTjspR8YCrxTsfSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"52","text":"3. Válvula de pliegue\\Ngastroesofágico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Válvula unidireccional.","guid":"xXsAm36FjkkhjJfQ3w9oNg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Abre cuando la presión intraesofágica excede la intragástrica.","guid":"IthoVDv4LF4V5Ejf8_7XHQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Cierra al colapsar sobre sí misma cuando la presión intragástrica excede la intraesofágica (16-17).","guid":"347OBYPQ1WcwZAmgpIAmJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"36","text":"Relajaciones transitorias del EEI\\N(rTEE):","guid":"ZahroLfJ-L-LjGBi9BJUIg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Relajación del EEI desencadenada por distensión gástrica (18-19).","guid":"qMz-LCFwAxwUz03j5Ey3Fg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Mecanismos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Relajación completa y prolongada del EEI.","guid":"LoSozPgChDmFbV6FpotCnw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"• Inhibición completa y prolongada del diafragma crural.","guid":"4O6GJ1JFBtGeKXQU9pC8Tg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"• Contracción del músculo longitudinal del esófago distal (18, 22-23).","guid":"VYnWD28vXyYfygWjuq1FXg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"• Asociada a reflujo gastroesofágico con mínima presión diferencial.","guid":"blvjitJR6WJAoh3enrreUQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"DISFUNCIÓN DE LA\\NBARRERA ANTIRREFLUJO","guid":"Pws8s7T7scSMGKZChpHZTQ","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Variables epidemiológicas:","guid":"GfDspWc6_EUNElaB6h6SUA","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Edad avanzada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"• Obesidad abdominal (24).","guid":"QVagehQztH0SFdDV_K0AoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"Asociación con hernia hiatal:","guid":"WIsVBVJV4evjau6OAG4Uaw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Mayor prevalencia y tamaño de la hernia ↔ presencia y severidad de esofagitis (25-26).","guid":"gRgAI74EPvlB7GOtuN1V9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"71","text":"Comprensión de la\\Nhernia hiatal:","guid":"oFSxmKH9S3jyyugZme8Abw","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Migración de la unión gastroesofágica o EEI desde su ubicación nativa (justo dentro y\\Ndebajo del diafragma) a una ubicación anormal (en o por encima del diafragma crural).","guid":"QxLK6aBXHBNg6COpv7D11Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"71","text":"Perturbaciones anatómicas\\Npotenciales:","guid":"eYyke1HWh1K6XRgJoXMrcw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Ensanchamiento del hiato diafragmático (27).","guid":"q1tl59LsbVp8bYiBNZCNXw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Atenuación del ligamento frenoesofágico.","guid":"WcvoB8RMjWsfC-3b1KBUsQ","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"• Pérdida del segmento intraabdominal del EEI distal.","guid":"1FmfKO2g3VIYtltsH6wvBg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"• Reposicionamiento del EEI en el mediastino.","guid":"NmFFznn_ZryiAgmjkW7rZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"71","text":"Consecuencias\\Nfisiológicas:","guid":"_jDZPmpQS23o8KDM5BpYOw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Función esfinteriana disminuida del diafragma crural durante inspiración y esfuerzo abdominal (28).","guid":"YQAT2zGH51HzSNWhF6ytAg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Pérdida de la capacidad del diafragma crural para prevenir reflujo durante la relajación del EEI inducida por deglución.","guid":"iFVHxdQeh075cvEMM5DYiw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"• Desactivación completa del mecanismo de válvula de pliegue.","guid":"4B07XjlhB0bhjSWdqc846g","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"• Debilitamiento del EEI intrínseco por cambios de presión durante el ciclo respiratorio (29).","guid":"TsGZA3Ike1JAHN7OXRCQiQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"• Aumento de la compliance de la unión gastroesofágica durante rTEE (dilatación del hiato).","guid":"q-WkQZ3d7yDPFLZCBY1q3g","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"• Umbral reducido para inducir rTEE en presencia de hernia hiatal (23).","guid":"OLyTXbvGi5-yGJqSZGbDMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"71","text":"Disrupción de la\\Nbarrera antirreflujo:","guid":"j-csSNJ7rd4Tr6xPsBVDDQ","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Reflejada en la distorsión anatómica de la unión esofagogástrica.","guid":"JFv8L66IHaqCv_42v5SXkw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• No siempre evidente radiográficamente como hernia hiatal manifiesta.","guid":"70gzyHprghm2-K_HJvqF8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"71","text":"Evaluación endoscópica\\Nde la disrupción:","guid":"kI4_0vVKaoepU_tPii2NPg","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Iniciativa de la American\\NForegut Society (AFS) (10):","guid":"Z4EWXCTLYEUXK-i02Is2VA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Evaluación de la integridad de la unión\\Nesofagogástrica en tres dominios:","guid":"gMWmYgaAfFAQEGNhCvmPwg","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"1. Longitud de la herniación axial.","guid":"DeXGqK8mOwXvKc36XXjCSg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"2. Diámetro del hiato diafragmático.","guid":"ElGBHFEPI-ZLuPh8fjS7AA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"3. Presencia/ausencia de la válvula de pliegue gastroesofágico.","guid":"UvcAYeaX_QmJWhbS0nXSxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"• Escala de graduación I-IV (solo grado I indica unión esofagogástrica intacta).","guid":"TgBYjHjHZJyN4YgPyTkMpw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"CARACTERÍSTICAS\\NDEL REFLUJO","guid":"u-sEmXYqTzaoooSajE13CQ","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Determinantes de la lesión\\Nmucosa esofágica:","guid":"Cr-IHEDCnJMIcoMSnDgVPg","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• pH intragástrico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Tiempo de contacto del reflujo con la mucosa esofágica.","guid":"kf6YXG5epd2JrDcRb6nv3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"Grado de daño mucoso:","guid":"4yIW0LI1U_gmedMHBm9geg","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Más significativo si:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"• pH del reflujo < 2.","guid":"_lVI3_21A4Q2Bj9R-Sz-7Q","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"• Presencia de pepsina en el reflujo.","guid":"PZuXZjA7MkTXlH5-ZwbXmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"• Ácidos biliares implicados en la esofagitis, especialmente en pacientes con reflujo duodenogástrico aumentado postcirugía gástrica (30).","guid":"ZoyAsknd9uVXkUgl8QLWnA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"0","text":"Manifestaciones clínicas del ERGE\\N(Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease)","guid":"4gth05ybI_ZPkSMSu0_OKA","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"1. Síntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Pirosis (Heartburn):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• Sensación de ardor en el área retroesternal, postprandial [2].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"• Problemática si ocurre ≥2 días/semana [2].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"111","text":"• Regurgitación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Percepción del flujo de contenido gástrico hacia la boca o hipofaringe [2].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Material ácido mezclado con alimentos no digeridos.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"110","text":"2. Síntomas adicionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Disfagia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• Común en pirosis crónica, puede indicar esofagitis por reflujo o estenosis esofágica [6].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"• Dolor torácico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Puede imitar angina pectoris, descrito como opresivo o ardor,\\Nsubesternal, radiando a espalda, cuello, mandíbula, brazos [1].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Duración: minutos a horas; resuelve espontáneamente o con antiácidos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Relacionado con comidas, despierta a pacientes, exacerbado por estrés emocional.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"• Pirosis es un predictor pobre de ERGE en dolor torácico (monitorización de pH esofágico) [7].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"118","text":"• Hipersalivación (Water brash):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Secreción de hasta 10 mL de saliva/minuto en respuesta al reflujo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"118","text":"• Sensación de globo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Percepción constante de bulto en la garganta, posible relación con ERGE [8].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"118","text":"• Náuseas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Infrecuente, considerar ERGE en náuseas inexplicables [9].","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Hallazgos\\Nradiográficos en\\NERGE","guid":"BIvUO9gIeXUKiQeDzhFFtA","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"1. Utilidad del examen de deglución\\Ncon bario de doble contraste:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• Limitado diagnóstico en ERGE:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Reflujo de bario: Significado dudoso (25-71% en sintomáticos; 20% en controles normales) [10].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• Precisión\\Ndiagnóstica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Esofagitis leve: 25%.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Esofagitis moderada: 82%.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Esofagitis severa: 99% [11].","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"132","text":"2. Cambios mucosos asociados con\\Nesofagitis y estenosis pépticas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Esofagitis por reflujo temprana:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• Mucosa del tercio distal del esófago granular/nodular, con lucencias mal definidas de 1-3 mm [12].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"• Esofagitis erosiva:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Úlceras superficiales y erosiones visibles como pequeñas acumulaciones de bario cerca\\Nde la unión gastroesofágica, rodeadas por halo radiolúcido de mucosa edematosa.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"• Estenosis\\Npéptica benigna:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Área de estrechamiento concéntrico y liso en el esófago distal\\N(1-4 cm de longitud; 0. 2-2.0 cm de diámetro).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"140","text":"• Estenosis asimétrica: Pared con cicatriz excéntrica.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones\\Ndel ERGE","guid":"w9NMZ1HuaTT-_V0VpEj7SA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"1. Esófago de Barrett.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"2. Estenosis esofágica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"3. Adenocarcinoma esofágico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"4. Complicaciones\\Nextraesofágicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• Laringitis crónica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Exacerbación de asma.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de ERGE (Enfermedad\\Npor Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"qC8IyTnC6nvyclYhaP9c4A","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"1. Pacientes con\\Nsíntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Pirosis y/o regurgitación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Dx basado en síntomas clínicos [2, 13].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Evaluación adicional\\Nsi presentan:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Signos de alarma.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Factores de riesgo para esófago de Barrett.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"• Imágenes GI anormales.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"156","text":"• Respuesta\\Na IBPs:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• 40-90% de pacientes con respuesta sintomática a IBPs.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• No criterio dx para ERGE [14,15].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"• Meta-análisis: Sensibilidad 78%, especificidad 54%.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"• No correlación con medidas objetivas (monitorización de pH ambulatorio) [15].","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"155","text":"2. Pacientes sin\\Nsíntomas clásicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• Otros síntomas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Dolor torácico, sensación de globo, tos crónica, ronquera, sibilancias, náuseas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• No suficientes para dx clínico de ERGE sin pirosis/regurgitación.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"• Excluir otros trastornos antes de\\Natribuir síntomas a ERGE:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Ej: Dolor torácico inexplicado → ECG y\\Nprueba de esfuerzo antes de evaluación GI.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación en pacientes seleccionados con ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"lwFBPlABkFNoZ4B_gbJKMw","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"Evaluación\\Nadicional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• Requerida en pacientes con\\Nsospecha de ERGE para:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Descartar etiologías alternativas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"• Confirmar el dx de ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"• Evaluar complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"174","text":"Endoscopia\\Ngastrointestinal alta:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• Evaluar signos de alarma o imágenes anormales (si no se realizó en los últimos 3 meses).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"• Cribado de esófago de Barrett en pacientes con factores de riesgo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"• Biopsias dirigidas a áreas de metaplasia, displasia o mucosa normal en ausencia de anomalías visibles\\N(para evaluar esofagitis eosinofílica) [16].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"181","text":"• No necesaria para dx de ERGE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"181","text":"• Detecta manifestaciones esofágicas de ERGE\\N(ej. Metaplasia de Barrett, esofagitis erosiva).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"181","text":"• Descartar malignidad del tracto GI superior.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"181","text":"• Descartar otras etiologías en síntomas refractarios a IBPs.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"180","text":"Características\\Nde alarma:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Sugieren\\Nmalignidad GI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"• Dispepsia de inicio reciente en ≥60 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"• Sangrado GI (hematemesis, melena, hematoquecia, sangre oculta en heces).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"• Anemia por deficiencia de hierro.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"• Anorexia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"• Pérdida de peso inexplicada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"• Disfagia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"190","text":"• Odinofagia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"190","text":"• Vómitos persistentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"190","text":"• Cáncer GI en un pariente de primer grado.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"174","text":"Factores de riesgo para\\Nesófago de Barrett:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"• Cribado recomendado para pacientes con múltiples factores de riesgo\\N(uno debe ser duración de ERGE ≥5-10 años).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"• Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"• Duración de ERGE ≥5-10 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"• Edad ≥50 años.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"• Sexo masculino.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"• Raza blanca.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"• Hernia hiatal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"• Obesidad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"• Reflujo nocturno.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"• Uso de tabaco (pasado o presente).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"• Pariente de primer grado con esófago de Barrett y/o adenocarcinoma.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"174","text":"Imágenes anormales del tracto\\Ngastrointestinal superior:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Imágenes abdominales no requeridas para dx de ERGE pero pueden ser realizadas para evaluar síntomas concurrentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"• Anomalías luminales en imágenes GI superiores pueden justificar evaluación diagnóstica con endoscopia GI alta.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"0","text":"Hallazgos endoscópicos en ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"CkayTG2kGwVMS280C1tFQw","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"1. Endoscopia\\Ngastrointestinal alta:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Pacientes\\Ncon ERGE:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"• Puede ser normal o mostrar esofagitis de diversos grados [17].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"• ~30% de pacientes no tratados presentan esofagitis endoscópica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"217","text":"• Severidad y duración de síntomas ≠ severidad de esofagitis.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"216","text":"• Esofagitis péptica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"• Ulceraciones: Forma irregular/lineal, múltiples, en esófago distal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"• Comparación: Esofagitis infecciosa/inducida por medicamentos → Ulceraciones en esófago medio.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"215","text":"2. Hallazgos endoscópicos\\Nen ERGE prolongado:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• Estenosis péptica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"• Metaplasia de Barrett.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"• Adenocarcinoma esofágico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"215","text":"3. Grado de severidad\\Nde esofagitis:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"• Esofagitis\\Nerosiva:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"• Grado según severidad para guiar el manejo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"• Clasificaciones endoscópicas para disminuir la variabilidad entre operadores.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"• Clasificación de Los Ángeles: Más evaluada y utilizada para esofagitis [18].","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"228","text":"• Clasificación de\\NLos Ángeles:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"General","guid":"","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• Evalúa severidad por extensión de anormalidad mucosa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"• Complicaciones registradas por separado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"• Ruptura mucosa: Área de desprendimiento adyacente a mucosa normal en epitelio escamoso, con/sin exudado.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"233","text":"• Grado A: Una o más rupturas mucosas, cada una ≤5 mm de longitud","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"233","text":"• Grado B: Al menos una ruptura mucosa >5 mm, no continua entre los pliegues mucosos adyacentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"233","text":"• Grado C: Al menos una ruptura mucosa continua entre los pliegues mucosos adyacentes, no circunferencial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"233","text":"• Grado D: Ruptura mucosa que involucra al menos tres cuartas partes de la circunferencia luminal","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial del ERGE\\N(Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofágico)","guid":"YncqKjxR48DidHMvE0GBmg","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"1. Esófagitis\\Ninfecciosa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Causas: Infección.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"243","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"242","text":"2. Esofagitis\\Npor pastillas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"• Causas: Medicamentos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"242","text":"3. Esofagitis\\Neosinofílica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"• Causas: Inflamación eosinofílica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"242","text":"4. Otras causas\\Nde disfagia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"• Anillos/webs esofágicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"• Peristalsis alterada (trastornos de motilidad esofágica).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"• Disfagia progresiva lenta para sólidos con obstrucción episódica → Estenosis o cáncer esofágico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"252","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"242","text":"5. Odinofagia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Causas: Esófagitis infecciosa o inducida por medicamentos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"• Dx: Manometría esofágica, endoscopia con biopsias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"242","text":"6. Hipótesis\\Nde reflujo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"• Hipersensibilidad\\Nal reflujo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Exposición ácida normal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"• Asociación de síntomas positiva con reflujo ácido o débilmente ácido.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"260","text":"• Pirosis funcional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Exposición ácida normal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"• Asociación de síntomas negativa con reflujo.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"260","text":"• Dx: Pruebas de pH o pH-impedancia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"242","text":"7. Dispepsia\\Nfuncional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Síntomas principales: Saciedad temprana, plenitud postprandial.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"• Pirosis en un tercio de los casos.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":270,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Gastroenterología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Gastroenterología","filename":"Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofagico-2024","id":"map_654","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Enfermedad por Reflujo Gastroesofagico-2024"}